Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.04,0:00:09.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,"NETFLIX\Nオリジナルシリーズ"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.51,0:00:18.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,♪〜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.91,0:00:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,ORIGINAL WORK BY RENSUKE OSHIKIRI
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.21,0:01:53.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,〜♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.52,0:02:04.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（台を叩く音）\N（マーくん）ウガアアー\Nまるで歯が立たねぇー！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.19,0:02:07.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,イライラをお前に歯を立てて\N解消したる！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.22,0:02:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I was completely powerless!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.09,0:02:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll vent my anger by hitting you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.99,0:02:09.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（男Ｂ）\Nなんスかなんスか もうっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.19,0:02:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing? Stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.96,0:02:10.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（マーくん）\Nラァアアアア
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.26,0:02:11.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（マーくん）\Nラァアアアア\N（男Ｂ）ちょっと！\Nやめて！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.39,0:02:12.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（マーくん）\Nラァアアアア\N（男Ｂ）ちょっと！\Nやめて！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.39,0:02:12.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大人がゲームで\N癇癪(かんしゃく)を起こしてモメてる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.39,0:02:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Adults fighting over a video game?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.46,0:02:14.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（マーくん）\Nラァアアアア
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.46,0:02:14.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大人がゲームで\N癇癪(かんしゃく)を起こしてモメてる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.70,0:02:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This place really is crude, right, Miyao?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.76,0:02:17.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やっぱりココは\N下劣な場所だな 宮尾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.80,0:02:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.90,0:02:19.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,って アレ？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.54,0:02:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Ono, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.64,0:02:22.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大野さん…　でしょ？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.87,0:02:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You transferred to Minami Middle School\Nyour third year?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.94,0:02:26.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（小春(こはる)）南中の３年の時\N１組に転校してきた…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.08,0:02:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I've seen you here plenty of times,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.14,0:02:31.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（小春）\Nなっ何度かこういうトコで\N見かけた事があるけど…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.35,0:02:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,but this is the first time\Nwe've talked like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.45,0:02:34.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こうして話すの…\N初めてだね…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.49,0:02:40.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,たっ対戦…\Nものすごく強いんだよね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.15,0:02:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You're really amazing at\Ncompetitive games, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.42,0:02:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So good, even I've heard the rumors.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.52,0:02:43.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,巷(ちまた)で噂に上がるくらい…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.69,0:02:46.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（小春）うう…\N何言ってんだろ 私…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.63,0:02:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What am I saying?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.86,0:02:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've heard she's extremely quiet.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.90,0:02:50.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ものすごく無口な子って\N聞いてたから…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.63,0:02:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have no idea what to talk about.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.67,0:02:52.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何話していいか\N全然分からない…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.14,0:02:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is the girl... Yaguchi...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.24,0:02:57.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この子が…　矢口君の…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.44,0:02:58.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（宮尾(みやお)）おーい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.64,0:02:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.84,0:03:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Long time no see, Hidaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.87,0:03:02.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,久しぶりだな 日高\Nあ…　あと大野さんも
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.91,0:03:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and you too, Ono.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.24,0:03:06.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（宮尾）\Nゲーセンとは無縁そうな\N２人が一緒にいるから
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.25,0:03:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's surprising to see the pair of you\Nat an arcade.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.15,0:03:08.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ビックリして\N話しかけちゃったよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.35,0:03:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It seemed so unlikely,\NI had to say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.75,0:03:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Was the last time you saw each other\Nthe middle school graduation?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.85,0:03:12.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２人とも\N中学を卒業して以来か…？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.22,0:03:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hidaka, I barely recognized you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.29,0:03:14.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,日高 見違えたな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.39,0:03:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Miyao...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.46,0:03:17.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（小春）\N宮尾君… 気を使って\N話しかけてくれたのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.56,0:03:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did he come talk to us{\i0}\N{\i1}'cause he cares for me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.73,0:03:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, and Ono's aura is as\Nmysterious as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.83,0:03:24.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（宮尾）\Nおっ大野さんも相変わらず―
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.77,0:03:27.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ミステリアスなオーラを\N放ってるね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.50,0:03:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What the heck am I saying?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.50,0:03:28.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（宮尾）\N何言ってんだ オレ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.04,0:03:29.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（小春）大野さん
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.04,0:03:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ono.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.47,0:03:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Since we're here,\Ncan I ask you for a match?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.51,0:03:33.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,せっかくだし\N私とお手合わせ願えるかな…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.11,0:03:38.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや…　やめた方がいいな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.14,0:03:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I wouldn't if I were you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.25,0:03:39.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（小春）え？　どうして？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.45,0:03:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, how come?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.95,0:03:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The adults are having a fist-less and\Nkick-less fight of shirt-pulling.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.98,0:03:42.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（宮尾）大人達がパンチや\Nキックではなく―
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.38,0:03:44.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,服を引っ張り合う\Nケンカをしている…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.72,0:03:48.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今日のところは諦めて\N帰った方がいい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.72,0:03:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You should probably just give up\Nand head home for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.26,0:03:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You... you may be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.32,0:03:50.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そ…　そうだね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.96,0:03:51.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（土井）大野さん
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.06,0:03:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ono!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.29,0:03:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me, Doi! Have you forgotten?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.33,0:03:55.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,僕だ！　土井だよ！\N忘れたのかい？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.10,0:03:58.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一緒の小学校でキラキラ\N光ってただろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.16,0:03:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We shined together in elementary school!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.67,0:03:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Doi...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.70,0:03:59.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,土井…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.80,0:04:02.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今もホラ！\Nキラキラ光ってるだろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.84,0:04:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,See, even now, I'm shining.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.37,0:04:05.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おおっ！\N覚えててくれたのかい？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.41,0:04:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so you do remember me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.51,0:04:08.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,遊ぼう！　さっそく\N遊ぼうじゃないか 大野さん
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.51,0:04:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's play. Let's play something, Ono!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.71,0:04:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go win some candy in your honor,\Nright now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.81,0:04:12.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今から君のために甘いアメを\NＧＥＴしてあげるからさ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.35,0:04:15.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（土井）ぐっ 取れねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.45,0:04:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.78,0:04:18.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,100円で10個アメ買った方が\Nよかったかな…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.85,0:04:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I have just bought\N10 candies for 100 yen?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.12,0:04:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say that. That would've been boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.15,0:04:21.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そういうつまんないこと\N言うなよな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.89,0:04:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, what happened to your medals\Nfrom earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.92,0:04:24.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それよりさっきのメダルは\Nどうした？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.29,0:04:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I handed them in to the shop.\NAll 50,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.33,0:04:26.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（土井）\N店に預けた…　５万枚…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.66,0:04:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If Yaguchi had gotten into{\i0}\N{\i1}Joran High School,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.83,0:04:30.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（小春）\N矢口君が\Nもし上蘭(じょうらん)に受かってたら
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.30,0:04:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}what kind of relationship would he and Ono{\i0}\N{\i1}have had?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.37,0:04:32.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今頃―
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.30,0:04:34.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大野さんとどういう関係に\Nなってたんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.67,0:04:38.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの矢口君にゲームを\Nガマンさせるくらい―
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.67,0:04:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She was able to get Yaguchi serious enough{\i0}\N{\i1}to hold off on games.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.87,0:04:40.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本気にさせる人…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.61,0:04:41.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ゴトン）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.74,0:04:44.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（土井）大野さん！\Nこのゲームで僕が勝ったら
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.24,0:04:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ono, if I win this game,\Ncome see a movie with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.75,0:04:46.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,映画を観に行こう！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.61,0:04:49.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,｢トイレの花子さん｣か\N｢耳をすませば｣！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.62,0:04:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Either{\i1} Hanako of the Toilet{\i0}\Nor {\i1}Whispers of the Heart.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.42,0:04:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with those choices?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.45,0:04:50.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（宮尾）なんだその２択
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.85,0:04:52.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ネットの音）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.16,0:04:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.29,0:04:55.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（土井）クソっ クソ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.89,0:04:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.82,0:04:59.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（土井）この絶妙な…\N距離が…　難しい！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.96,0:04:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This distance makes it hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.23,0:05:04.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ねえ 大野さん
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.37,0:05:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ono.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.80,0:05:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you seen Yaguchi, lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.87,0:05:08.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（小春）最近 矢口君と\N顔合わせてる？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.57,0:05:10.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（衝突音）\N（晶）！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.27,0:05:12.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（宮尾･小春）うわっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.61,0:05:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It hit her square in the face.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.67,0:05:14.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,モロに顔面イッたな オイ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.64,0:05:16.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（宮尾）\N今のが１人だったら―
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.94,0:05:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If you had been alone, that could've been\Nso embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.28,0:05:18.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,恥ずかしくて\N大惨事になってたぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.35,0:05:22.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも…　ドジった時も\Nチャームだな 大野さんは…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.35,0:05:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're still charming,\Neven when you have a clumsy moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.08,0:05:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying, Miyao?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.25,0:05:25.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何言ってんのよ宮尾君
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.55,0:05:27.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,鼻とか歯が折れてたら\Nどーするの！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.55,0:05:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What if she'd broken her nose\Nor teeth or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.69,0:05:31.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（宮尾）ちょ…\N本当に大丈夫か 大野さん…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.69,0:05:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you're okay, Ono?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.46,0:05:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.59,0:05:32.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,って…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.93,0:05:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,moving on to {\i1}Virtua Cop?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.16,0:05:36.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（宮尾）\N｢バーチャコップ｣を\Nやるのかい？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.70,0:05:41.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんかフラフラしてるし…\N今日はもう帰った方が…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.73,0:05:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, you seem kind of dazed,\NMaybe you should head home for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.97,0:05:43.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（コイン投入音）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.27,0:05:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll play with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.34,0:05:45.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（小春）私も一緒にやる
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.38,0:05:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Two beautiful girls cooperating\Nin a shooting game?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.51,0:05:48.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（宮尾）えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.91,0:05:49.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（宮尾）えっ？\N（土井）おお！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.31,0:05:49.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（土井）おお！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.84,0:05:53.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（土井）麗しき女子の\N共同銃撃戦！　見ものだな…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.48,0:05:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,A sight to behold.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.05,0:05:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is crazy. This is crazy, Haruo!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.22,0:05:57.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（宮尾）えらいこっちゃ…\Nえらいこっちゃやで 春雄！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.42,0:06:01.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ゲーム音）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.32,0:06:03.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（小春）あ！　スゴイ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.36,0:06:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, wow.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.89,0:06:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It takes me two or three shots{\i0}\N{\i1}to take down an enemy{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.06,0:06:07.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,敵を１人倒すのに\N私が２〜３発に対して―
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.36,0:06:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}while Ono kills them all with one.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.36,0:06:09.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大野さんは確実に１発で\N仕留めてる…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.53,0:06:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So calm and composed,{\i0}\N{\i1}with no wasted movement.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.63,0:06:12.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,冷静沈着でムダがなく
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.93,0:06:14.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,手際がよくて
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.93,0:06:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Such dexterity.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.37,0:06:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's a little hard to approach,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.54,0:06:16.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょっととっつきにくい\Nところがあるけど
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.00,0:06:20.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本当に綺麗(きれい)…\Nでもどこか陰があるような…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.04,0:06:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but she's so beautiful.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.91,0:06:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But she seems to have a dark side too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.58,0:06:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I... want to know what{\i0}\N{\i1}she's really thinking.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.68,0:06:23.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私 この人の本音が\N知りたい…！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.65,0:06:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ono...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.78,0:06:25.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大野さん
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.05,0:06:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you feel about Yaguchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.12,0:06:29.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（小春）矢口君のこと\Nどう思ってるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.45,0:06:31.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（土井）おおっと！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.95,0:06:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.39,0:06:34.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大野さんが一般人を\N誤殺してしまったぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.45,0:06:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ono shot a civilian!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.22,0:06:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Since being rejected\Nby Joran High School,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.32,0:06:36.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,上蘭高校に落ちてから―
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.96,0:06:39.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,矢口君 引け目を\N感じてるみたいなの
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.26,0:06:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yaguchi has had an inferiority complex.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.06,0:06:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Toward you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.23,0:06:41.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大野さんに対して…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.66,0:06:43.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（土井）おおっと！　また！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.70,0:06:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! Not again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.87,0:06:45.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何を話してるんだ 二人は…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.87,0:06:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what they're talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.74,0:06:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I think he's distanced himself\Nfrom arcades,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.77,0:06:50.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しばらくゲーセンからも\N足が遠のいていたのも
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.64,0:06:53.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大野さんと会うのを\N怖がってたからだと思うの…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.64,0:06:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,because he was afraid of facing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.31,0:06:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He's always on the lookout and on edge\Nwhen he comes here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.38,0:06:56.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここに来るといつも\Nキョロキョロしたり
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.58,0:06:57.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おどおどしたり…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.31,0:06:58.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（小春）ねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.41,0:06:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.45,0:07:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,tell me how you really feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.52,0:07:02.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大野さんの\N本当の気持ちを教えて
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.15,0:07:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeing how Yaguchi is now,\NI feel so sorry for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.25,0:07:06.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今の矢口君を見てると\Nかわいそうで仕方ないの
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.86,0:07:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're not concerned for him...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.09,0:07:10.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もし大野さんが\N矢口君に対して関心がなく
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.96,0:07:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't feel anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.06,0:07:12.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何も感じてないのであれば…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.03,0:07:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,then I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.09,0:07:14.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（小春）私が矢口君に…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.23,0:07:15.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.83,0:07:22.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（射撃音）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.01,0:07:26.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ゲーム音声）\Nうおっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.31,0:07:29.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.41,0:07:32.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すごいな 大野さん！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.41,0:07:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You're amazing, Ono!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.55,0:07:36.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大野さんがこんなにゲームが\N上手だったなんて驚きさぁ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.08,0:07:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you're so good at games!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.19,0:07:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm seriously no match at all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.32,0:07:39.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（小春）ホント…\Nまるで敵わない…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.22,0:07:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But I wonder how I'd fare\Nif it were a fighting game.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.25,0:07:43.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも対戦格闘ゲームだったら\Nどんな勝負に…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.43,0:07:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well, until we meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.49,0:07:46.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（宮尾）じゃ…\Nじゃあまた会えたら
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.03,0:07:48.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大野さんも気をつけて\N帰って…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.03,0:07:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Go home safely, Ono.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.00,0:07:51.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（土井）ハッハッハッ\N気をつけたまえー
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.47,0:07:54.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（土井）ハッハッハッ\N気をつけたまえー
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.47,0:07:54.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（宮尾）\Nふぅ…　穏便にすんだか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.47,0:07:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Things stayed amicable, thank goodness.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.07,0:07:54.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（宮尾）\Nふぅ…　穏便にすんだか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.37,0:07:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why am I being so considerate, Haruo?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.40,0:07:57.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（宮尾）\Nなんで俺がこんなに\N気を使ってるんだ 春雄君…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.47,0:08:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What am I doing?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.54,0:08:01.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（小春）\N私何やってんだろ\N初めて話す子に…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.78,0:08:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I spoke to her for the first time,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.68,0:08:05.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかもゲームプレイ中に\Nあんな事聞くなんて…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.71,0:08:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and I asked her all that mid-game, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.78,0:08:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.88,0:08:07.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（萌美(もえみ)）晶さん
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.55,0:08:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems your awful habits\Nhave continued into high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.65,0:08:11.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アナタの悪趣味は\N高等学校に上がった今でも―
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.89,0:08:13.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,続いているようですね…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.39,0:08:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,As the daughter of the Ono conglomerate,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.42,0:08:16.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大野財閥の\N令嬢の身でありながら
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.99,0:08:20.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あんな場所に出入りするなど\N言語道断です
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.99,0:08:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,for you to frequent such a place\Nis inconceivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.26,0:08:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Miss Goda. It may seem like\Na distasteful hobby to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.33,0:08:24.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（爺や）\Nあ あの…　業田先生には\N悪趣味に見えると思いますが
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.33,0:08:26.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お嬢様にとっては\Nささやかな楽しみ…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.37,0:08:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,but to the Young Miss,\Nit's a modest past time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.14,0:08:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's her one interest that puts her\Nat ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.20,0:08:30.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（爺や）心の支え…\N唯一の趣味でございます…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.31,0:08:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If she were to turn delinquent and spend\Nall her time there, that's one thing--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.37,0:08:31.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,グレて不良娘になって
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.97,0:08:34.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ゲーセンに入り浸るなら\Nともかくですね…　あ…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.81,0:08:38.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（萌美）いえ 盛り場に\N行く事自体が問題行動
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.84,0:08:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.88,0:08:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Going to degenerate places in itself\Nis unacceptable.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.88,0:08:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a symptom of delinquency.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.91,0:08:40.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,グレる兆候とみます
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.58,0:08:44.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（爺や）な ならば…\N家庭用の据え置き機の購入を
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.62,0:08:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,T-Then consider buying her\Na console for home--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.99,0:08:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.15,0:08:45.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（萌美）何ですの それは
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.52,0:08:47.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（爺や）プレステとか\Nサターンとか…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.75,0:08:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a PlayStation or Saturn,\Nor the upcoming  Virtual Boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.29,0:08:49.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今度発売する\Nバーチャルボーイとか…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.99,0:08:52.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ゲームのことなんて\Nまったく分かりません
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.03,0:08:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know a single thing about games!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.49,0:08:56.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,先生！　バーチャルボーイ\N買って差し上げましょうよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.49,0:08:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Goda, please let's buy\Na Virtual Boy for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.63,0:08:58.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私も欲しいからぁ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.73,0:08:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I want one, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.13,0:08:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We shall not.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.17,0:08:58.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（萌美）なりません
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.00,0:09:01.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（爺や）\Nお願いします！　バーチャ…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.27,0:09:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.84,0:09:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,-Please--\N-Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.30,0:09:02.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（萌美）うるさい！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.67,0:09:04.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（転がる音）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.01,0:09:07.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ローで持ってかれたか…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.01,0:09:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That low kick got the best of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.44,0:09:11.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大野家の指南役を\N務めさせて頂くこの業田萌美
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.78,0:09:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I, Moemi Goda, instructor\Nof the Ono family,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.68,0:09:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,do not make compromises.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.75,0:09:13.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,甘えや妥協は絶対許しません
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.12,0:09:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I will watch over her closely\Nin her most vulnerable high school years.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.42,0:09:18.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,高校生という子供達が\N一番危うい時期を
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.39,0:09:20.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しっかり管理させて頂きます
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.76,0:09:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I have made your parents promise\Nnot to give you even one yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.82,0:09:23.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（萌美）お母様方には―
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.32,0:09:26.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１円たりとも金銭を\N渡さないことを約束させます
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.93,0:09:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't have you even playing the\Nten-yen rock-paper-scissors game.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.16,0:09:28.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,10円でできる―
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.20,0:09:30.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ジャンケンマンすら\N許しませんから
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.23,0:09:31.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょっと知ってるじゃん…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.40,0:09:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you do know a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.30,0:09:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Your curfew is 4 p.m.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.37,0:09:33.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,門限は午後４時
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.44,0:09:36.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,学校からの直帰は厳守！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.44,0:09:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You must come straight home from school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.70,0:09:40.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（爺や）\Nそっそれでは ご友人との\N親交もままならなく…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.74,0:09:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,She won't be able to build relationships\Nwith her friends that way...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.11,0:09:42.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,結構毛だらけ\N猫灰だらけですわ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.14,0:09:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine. Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.24,0:09:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Conversing with them at school\Nshould be plenty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.44,0:09:45.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ご友人との交流は\N校内で十分…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.41,0:09:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Romantic relationships with boys\Nis out of the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.51,0:09:49.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（萌美）男子との交流…\N恋愛なんてもってのほか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.85,0:09:54.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,高校を卒業して一流大学に\N入学して勉学に専念したのち
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.85,0:09:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you've graduated and begun studying\Nat a top-class college,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.72,0:09:57.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,決められた男性との結婚が\N控えているのです
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.76,0:09:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,your parents will choose your husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.66,0:10:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the will of your father\Nand mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.79,0:09:59.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それが―
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.79,0:10:02.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アナタのお父様とお母様の\N御意思なのです！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.20,0:10:04.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（犬の鳴き声）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.50,0:10:07.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ゲーム音）\N（春雄）クックックッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.00,0:10:11.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この体勢で100面まで\Nクリアしたぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.57,0:10:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I've cleared 100 levels in this position.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.11,0:10:14.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,初心に返る以上のことを\N成した気分だぜ…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.14,0:10:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I've regained my roots\Nand then some.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.04,0:10:17.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）まあ…\N感覚がおかしくなって
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.08,0:10:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,My senses are so messed up, it might\Nhave an opposite effect on other games.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.11,0:10:21.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,他のゲームに逆効果な\N気がするがよしとしよう
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.25,0:10:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.45,0:10:25.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,極め付けは同じクラスの\N金持ちの小林君から借りた―
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.45,0:10:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I borrowed this beauty, the Neo Geo CD\Nfrom Kobayashi, the rich kid in my class.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.49,0:10:26.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,｢ネオジオＣＤ｣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.92,0:10:31.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これでいくらでも家庭内で\N武者修行が可能になった
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.12,0:10:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,With this I can get as much\Nintensive training as I want at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.69,0:10:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What'll happen if I can practice endlessly\Nwithout worrying about money?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.73,0:10:34.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この俺が金銭を\N気にしないで―
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.23,0:10:36.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,際限なく\N練習したらどうなるか…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.27,0:10:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure I'll leave her dumbfounded with\Nmy superhuman ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.33,0:10:40.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,きっと度肝を抜く\N超人的強さになって
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.37,0:10:43.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,日高も気絶するに\N決まってらぁ〜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.37,0:10:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Hidaka will faint from shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.27,0:10:50.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふふふふ…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.09,0:11:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Achoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.19,0:11:05.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（なみえ）ハクション！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.69,0:11:07.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（鼻をすする音）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.87,0:11:14.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）\Nう〜ん　ふふふふ…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.41,0:11:24.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（犬の鳴き声）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.88,0:11:28.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,んんん…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.45,0:11:39.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（猫の鳴き声）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.93,0:11:48.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なっ長い…！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.50,0:11:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It takes so long!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.28,0:12:03.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大野家令嬢としての使命を\Nまっとうすること…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.32,0:12:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,As daughter of the Ono family,\Nyou must take your duties seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.82,0:12:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.85,0:12:05.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,受け入れるのです
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.65,0:12:07.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（萌美）\Nプライベートは皆無と\N思いなさい…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.65,0:12:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You don't get to have a private life!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.96,0:12:11.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,矢口君…\N引け目を感じてるみたいなの
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.96,0:12:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yaguchi seems to have\Nan inferiority complex, toward you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.13,0:12:13.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大野さんに対して…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.83,0:12:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tell me, how you really feel?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.90,0:12:17.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（小春）\N大野さんの本当の気持ちを\N教えて…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.94,0:12:28.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（こらえ泣き）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.02,0:12:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,JULY 1995
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.06,0:12:49.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（セミの鳴き声）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.46,0:12:52.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ゲーム音）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.67,0:12:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's not here either.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.70,0:12:55.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）ここにもいねーか…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.77,0:13:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's already been a week since I got{\i0}\N{\i1}my feel and confidence back.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.90,0:12:59.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,感覚と自信と取り戻してから\N早１週間…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.21,0:13:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've searched all the arcades{\i0}\N{\i1}and candy shops I could think of,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.27,0:13:03.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,思い当たる近所のゲーセンや\N駄菓子屋を探しまくってるが
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.81,0:13:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but I still haven't seen Ono.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.88,0:13:05.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いまだに大野の姿が\N見当たらん…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.08,0:13:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm finally in the right mindset{\i0}\N{\i1}to meet her,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.11,0:13:09.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,せっかく面と向かえる\N気になれたのに…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.18,0:13:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}what's going on?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.35,0:13:11.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんだってんだよ…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.82,0:13:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'd always see her car parked outside{\i0}\N{\i1}arcades before...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.89,0:13:15.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,前はしょっちゅう\N大野ん家の車が―
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.19,0:13:17.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ゲーセン前で停まってるのを\N見かけたのに…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.86,0:13:20.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ゲーム音声）\Nきゃあ〜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.89,0:13:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,MATCH OVER
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.56,0:13:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,A 21-win streak.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.60,0:13:22.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（小春）21連勝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.60,0:13:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like he's back in form.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.66,0:13:26.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すっかり昔の勘を\N取り戻したってワケね…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.07,0:13:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,See, Hidaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.13,0:13:29.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おう 日高\Nお前に言われた通り―
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.67,0:13:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I've made a full recovery after starting\Nover from {\i1}Yie Ar Kung-Fu {\i0}like you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.04,0:13:33.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,｢イー･アル･カンフー｣から\Nやり直して完全復活したぜ…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.87,0:13:36.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ネオジオＣＤでの修行で\N腕はもちろん―
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.01,0:13:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Through my training with the Neo Geo CD,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.98,0:13:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I've elevated not only my skill,\Nbut patience as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.01,0:13:39.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,忍耐力まで\N上げまくったからなー
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.11,0:13:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to the load time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.21,0:13:41.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ロード時間によって
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.58,0:13:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Load time?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.62,0:13:42.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ロード時間？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.28,0:13:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall I repay you for the disgrace\Nyou wrought upon me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.35,0:13:47.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前に受けた屈辱 今ここで\N晴らさせてもらおうか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.29,0:13:49.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして俺はもっともっと\N前へ行く！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.32,0:13:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll go even further ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.09,0:13:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, come at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.12,0:13:52.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ホラかかってこいや
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.36,0:13:53.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺の超人的強さで―
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.39,0:13:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make you faint while coughing up\Nblood with my super-human ability...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.79,0:13:56.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,吐血しながら\N気絶させてやっからよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.63,0:13:57.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やーだよー
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.63,0:13:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.90,0:13:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.03,0:13:58.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なぬっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.93,0:14:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not afraid of losing...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.97,0:14:00.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,負ける気はしないけど…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.00,0:14:03.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まだ矢口君の優位に\N立っていたいしね
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.00,0:14:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'd like to reign as champion\Nfor a while longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.81,0:14:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not fair, Hidaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.87,0:14:04.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,汚いぞ日高！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.34,0:14:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And by "further ahead",{\i0}\N{\i1}you mean Ono, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.41,0:14:08.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（小春）\Nそれに…　“前”って\N大野さんのことでしょ？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.04,0:14:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I felt like watching from behind\Ntoday anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.11,0:14:11.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（小春）ま 今日はうしろで\N見てたい気分だし…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.75,0:14:14.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）そーかい！\N100連勝すっから―
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.78,0:14:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That so? Then shrink in fear as I clear\Na 100-win streak.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.35,0:14:15.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,尻込みすればいいさ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.75,0:14:16.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ゲーム音声）\Nぎゃ〜〜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.18,0:14:17.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ゲーム音声）\Nぎゃ〜〜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.18,0:14:17.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）\Nあーやられた
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.22,0:14:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, he got me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.16,0:14:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You're such a hard worker, Yaguchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.19,0:14:26.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（おばちゃん）\N矢口君はよく働くねぇ…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.93,0:14:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there something you want to buy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.96,0:14:28.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何か買いたいものでも\Nあるのー？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.20,0:14:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,A Virtual Boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.26,0:14:30.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バーチャルボーイっす
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.70,0:14:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandma's boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.73,0:14:31.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ばーちゃんぼーい？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.57,0:14:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Could it be...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.60,0:14:38.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）\Nもしかして…　あいつ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.64,0:14:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}she got tired of it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.67,0:14:39.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,飽きたのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.04,0:14:41.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（なみえ）\Nねーねー 春雄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.24,0:14:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Haruo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.88,0:14:44.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,夏休み一緒に映画行かない？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.88,0:14:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to see a movie with me over\Nsummer break?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.58,0:14:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Haunted School?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.68,0:14:45.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,｢学校の怪談｣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.28,0:14:47.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えー うん…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.28,0:14:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.68,0:14:51.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）\N｢ザ･キング･オブ･\Nファイターズ95｣も―
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.75,0:14:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The King of Fighters '95 is{\i0}\N{\i1}coming out soon{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.25,0:14:52.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もうすぐ出るし
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.15,0:14:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and I hear Tekken 2 is coming in August,{\i0}\N{\i1}too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.32,0:14:54.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,｢鉄拳２｣も８月に出ると\N聞く…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.53,0:15:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All these amazing games are coming out,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.66,0:15:00.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どんどんスゲー新作が\N出てくるっていうのに
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.13,0:15:03.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大野は何やってんだ…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.16,0:15:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}what is Ono thinking?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.70,0:15:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did something happen at home?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.80,0:15:07.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,家で何かあったのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.54,0:15:10.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,張り合いが\Nなくなっちまうな…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.54,0:15:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is killing my buzz.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.47,0:15:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I mean, what have I even been doing{\i0}\N{\i1}all this time?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.51,0:15:14.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,っていうか\N今まで俺は何やってきたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.34,0:15:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,"I don't have the right to face her"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.44,0:15:18.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,合わせる顔がねーとか\Nゼロからやり直すとか…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.11,0:15:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and "starting over from zero"...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.15,0:15:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Why am I just going in circles like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.18,0:15:24.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんで俺はこうも\N空回りしちまうんだろうなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.47,0:15:40.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.64,0:15:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.60,0:15:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Young master, Yaguchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.64,0:15:44.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,矢口のお坊ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.67,0:15:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's the old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.74,0:15:46.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,爺やじゃねーかよ…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.14,0:15:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It has been a long time, lad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.27,0:15:49.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お久し振りでございます\Nお坊ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.08,0:15:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You're... alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.81,0:15:51.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ん？　１人…　なのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.48,0:15:54.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その様子を見ると\Nここではないのですな…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.48,0:15:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're also looking for her\Nthen she must not be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.68,0:15:55.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,え？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.58,0:15:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Ono ran away?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.65,0:15:58.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）大野が家出！？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.79,0:16:01.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はい…　御家での\Nお嬢様に対しての躾(しつけ)が―
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.82,0:16:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, her discipline had become too strict\Nand then she ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.99,0:16:03.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,厳しくなっておりまして…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.23,0:16:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Discipline?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.29,0:16:05.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）躾(しつけ)…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.49,0:16:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Her curfew starts at 4 p.m.,\Nshe was to come straight home from school.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.53,0:16:07.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,門限は午後４時
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.53,0:16:09.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,学校が終わればほぼ直帰…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.63,0:16:11.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ご趣味の盛り場へ\N出向くことも―
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.70,0:16:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,She was unable to go to the places\Nshe enjoyed as she pleased.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.90,0:16:13.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ままならなくなり
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.37,0:16:16.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お嬢様は息が詰まる日々を\N過ごしておりました
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.40,0:16:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The Young Miss was going through her days\Nwith little room to breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.37,0:16:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd worried something like this\Nwould happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.44,0:16:20.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私もこうなるのではと\N危惧(きぐ)していたのです
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.01,0:16:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,"Is she going to run away?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.11,0:16:23.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,家出するんじゃないかな〜？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.14,0:16:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, oh, no. This is bad, I'm scared."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.18,0:16:26.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,嫌だな嫌だな\Nヤバイな〜怖いな〜って…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.32,0:16:30.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（爺や）朝から忽然(こつぜん)と\N行方知れずになり―
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.32,0:16:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We suddenly lost track of her this morning
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.92,0:16:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and now it's almost evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.95,0:16:34.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう今は夕方近く…\N手には何も持たず
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.12,0:16:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,She didn't take anything with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.22,0:16:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,She's likely almost out of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.39,0:16:37.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おそらく所持金もわずか…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.39,0:16:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going crazy worrying about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.42,0:16:39.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,心配で心配で\Nおかしくなりそうです
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.96,0:16:42.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,高校に入ってから御友人も―
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.26,0:16:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems she hasn't been able to make\Nfriends since entering high school either.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.96,0:16:45.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お作りになっていない\Nようですし…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.77,0:16:48.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,手掛かりはお坊ちゃんだけ\Nだったのですが
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.80,0:16:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You were the only lead I had.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.17,0:16:51.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お嬢様の行きそうな場所に―
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.24,0:16:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any idea where she might be?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.47,0:16:53.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何か心当たりは\Nございませんか？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.64,0:16:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Somewhere that might hold\Nmemories for her?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.71,0:16:58.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お嬢様の\N思い入れがあるような場所は
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.85,0:17:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, no...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.88,0:17:00.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）いやいや
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.08,0:17:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why does Andre's chain-link stage{\i0}\N{\i1}come to mind?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.15,0:17:03.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アンドレの金網ステージが\Nなんで出てくんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.42,0:17:06.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,地獄じゃねえ 地獄じゃねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.45,0:17:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not hell either!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.62,0:17:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't think of anything!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.65,0:17:08.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まるで思いつかねぇ…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.49,0:17:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can only think of unrealistic places!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.49,0:17:11.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,出てくる場所は\N非現実的なものばかり…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.86,0:17:15.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やっぱ\Nアイツが行く所っていったら
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.86,0:17:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The place she'd go would have to be...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.16,0:17:19.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,近所のゲーセンは\Nだいたい見てみたが―
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.30,0:17:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've looked at all the neighborhood{\i0}\N{\i1}arcades, so I doubt she's there.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.83,0:17:21.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いるワケねーか…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.70,0:17:23.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わざわざ爺やに\N見つかるような所に―
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.74,0:17:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's not dumb enough to run away to{\i0}\N{\i1}a place where the old man would find her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.97,0:17:25.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,家出するほど\Nバカじゃねぇよな…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.78,0:17:31.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やっぱり 修行なんてしてる\N場合じゃなかった…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.78,0:17:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I guess it wasn't the time for me to be{\i0}\N{\i1}training after all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.41,0:17:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I had gone to see her sooner...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.45,0:17:33.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もっと早くアイツに\N会っていれば…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.35,0:17:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.42,0:17:38.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや 大野も一人で\Nいたいだけなのかもしれん…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.58,0:17:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ono might just want to be alone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.65,0:17:40.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,動くことを\N躊躇(ちゅうちょ)させられるぜ…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.69,0:17:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That makes me reluctant to look for her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.29,0:17:43.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でじゃばりって\N思われるかもしれねーし…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.29,0:17:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She might see me as nosy...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.26,0:17:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And it's not like I can do anything about{\i0}\N{\i1}Ono's home situation either.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.32,0:17:47.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だいたい俺なんかが\N大野んちの事情を―
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.53,0:17:49.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんとかしてやれる\Nワケでもないしな…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.93,0:17:54.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お坊ちゃんはお嬢様の\N唯一の御友人でしょお！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.30,0:17:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You are the Young Miss's only friend, lad!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.57,0:17:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you just going to space out and play\Nyour Virtual Boy now that she's run away?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.67,0:17:55.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,家でボーっと\Nバーチャルボーイをやってる
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.30,0:17:57.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,家でボーっと\Nバーチャルボーイをやってる
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.30,0:17:57.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）まだ買ってない\Nまだ買ってない！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.91,0:17:57.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）まだ買ってない\Nまだ買ってない！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.97,0:17:59.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）まだ買ってない\Nまだ買ってない！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.97,0:17:59.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おつもりですかーっ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.74,0:18:01.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ゲーム音）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.41,0:18:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well, I've still got a couple of ideas.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.44,0:18:03.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）まあ まだ\N思い当たるふしはある
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.41,0:18:07.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,地元からある程度離れていて\Nゲーセンが多い所…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.51,0:18:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Like places further away from home{\i0}\N{\i1}with lots of arcades.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.32,0:18:11.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,所持金が少ないということを\N考えて行ける所といったら…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.35,0:18:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A place she'd go if she didn't have much{\i0}\N{\i1}pocket money.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.55,0:18:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,KAWASAKI
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.39,0:18:14.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここしかない…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.49,0:18:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It'd have to be here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.72,0:18:17.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一度一緒に来たことが\Nあるしな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.72,0:18:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We came here together once, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.63,0:18:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I ran away from home,{\i0}\N{\i1}I'd come to this town.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.69,0:18:21.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺も家出するならこの町に\N出向くぜ…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.80,0:18:24.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ゲーセンの数も\N置いてある種類も―
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.80,0:18:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's a lot of arcades here with{\i0}\N{\i1}a ton of games.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.06,0:18:25.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハンパねーからな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.87,0:18:27.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ゲームショップも\Nまぁまぁある
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.90,0:18:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There are plenty of game shops as well.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.90,0:18:29.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うほほ〜い！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.90,0:18:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! I love dirty-looking shops like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.30,0:18:33.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こういう汚い感じの店は\N大好物だぜ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.54,0:18:35.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ニューファミコンが\Nあるじゃねぇか！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.57,0:18:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,They have the NES!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.28,0:18:37.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さすが川崎！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.34,0:18:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Kawasaki delivers--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.44,0:18:38.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（衝撃音）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.21,0:18:38.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ガイル）\N春雄！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.25,0:18:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Haruo! Is that what you're here to find?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.98,0:18:41.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前が捜しているものは\Nソレなのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.65,0:18:42.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）ちがいます
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.82,0:18:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.02,0:18:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Looking for someone who may or{\i0}\N{\i1}may not even be here{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.05,0:18:46.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この広い街でいるかどうか\Nわかんねー奴を捜すのも―
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.49,0:18:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}in a huge town like this is reckless,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.35,0:18:47.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,かなり無謀だが…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.36,0:18:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but I'll take it a step at a time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.42,0:18:48.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,地道に行くか…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.99,0:18:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've been here enough times{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.06,0:18:51.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,川崎のゲーセンは\N網羅しているからな…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.63,0:18:54.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,置いてるゲームの種類も\Nなんとなく把握している
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.66,0:18:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to know where everything is{\i0}\N{\i1}and what games they have.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.40,0:18:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is Ono feeling right now?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.53,0:18:58.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大野は今\Nどんな気分でいるかな…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.27,0:18:59.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,家に閉じ込められた事で―
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.03,0:19:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In order to release the built-up stress{\i0}\N{\i1}of being confined at home,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.03,0:19:02.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,溜まり溜まったものを\N発散させるため
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.64,0:19:05.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,体感型ゲーム機が\N多く置かれている店に―
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.67,0:19:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}she might've gone to an arcade with lots{\i0}\N{\i1}of physically demanding machines.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.17,0:19:06.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いるかもしれん
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.14,0:19:08.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はたまた家出した事で\Nナーバスになり…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.17,0:19:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Or she could've gotten anxiety from{\i0}\N{\i1}everything at home,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.74,0:19:09.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何も考えなくても出来る
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.78,0:19:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and gone to a medal arcade where you don't{\i0}\N{\i1}have to think.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.04,0:19:11.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,メダルゲーセンにいるやも…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.71,0:19:13.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うぐっ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.38,0:19:16.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ダルシム）\N長〜く遊べるゲームを\Nやってるかもよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.38,0:19:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She might be playing a game{\i0}\N{\i1}that would last a while.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.22,0:19:17.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.22,0:19:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.08,0:19:19.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）\N持ち金が少ない状況なら―
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.49,0:19:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Without much money,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.25,0:19:21.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,長く遊べるゲームに\Nすがるのは自然な行為！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.29,0:19:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}it's natural she'd go for a game{\i0}\N{\i1}with a longer duration!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.96,0:19:23.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺ならそうする…！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.02,0:19:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's what I'd do!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.96,0:19:26.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大野の得意な\N｢ファイナルファイト｣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.03,0:19:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ono's specialty, Final Fight.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.89,0:19:29.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あとは｢マジックソード｣に\N｢カダッシュ｣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.93,0:19:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Or maybe Magic Sword or Cadash.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.03,0:19:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Some kind of side-scroller{\i0}\N{\i1}is the most plausible.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.06,0:19:31.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,横スクロールアクションが\N有力だ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.33,0:19:33.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それらが置いていそうな\Nゲーセン…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.33,0:19:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}An arcade with lots of those...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.93,0:19:36.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まずはそこから捜してみっか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.93,0:19:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll try searching from there first.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.37,0:19:39.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ！\Nモータルコンバット２と３！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.60,0:19:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh! Mortal Kombat II and III!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.17,0:19:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pistol Daimyo no Boken!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.21,0:19:42.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ピストル大名の大冒険！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.28,0:19:46.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ…　この脳みそを\Nとろけさせる世界観！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.08,0:19:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The bewitching design of this world!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.58,0:19:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Look at the show it puts on!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.58,0:19:48.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見よ…　このやられ姿！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.48,0:19:50.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大野に見せてやりてーぜ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.92,0:19:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to show Ono!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.48,0:19:51.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（衝撃音）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.29,0:19:51.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ダルシム）\N春雄！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.32,0:19:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Haruo!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.05,0:19:52.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）ゴッ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.92,0:19:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}T-This is bad.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.99,0:19:57.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）だっダメだ…\Nついつい遊んでしまった！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.69,0:19:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I started playing without thinking.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.06,0:20:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}These alluring games are trifling with me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.09,0:20:00.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,魅惑なゲームに\Nすぐ翻弄されちまう…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.70,0:20:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is as tough as a panda trying{\i0}\N{\i1}to ignore bamboo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.73,0:20:03.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,パンダが笹の葉トンネルを\N素通りするくらいの―
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.30,0:20:04.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,難関っぷり…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.04,0:20:09.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すでに８時
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.07,0:20:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's already 8 p.m.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.54,0:20:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The town has started to shift{\i0}\N{\i1}into nightlife.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.60,0:20:12.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本格的に街が夜の顔を\N見せてきたぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.67,0:20:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The adults' time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.71,0:20:14.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大人達の時間…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.08,0:20:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And with it comes danger.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.31,0:20:18.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして同時に危険性も\N増してくる…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.61,0:20:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Will that little princess be okay{\i0}\N{\i1}on her own?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.78,0:20:22.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんなところで\Nお嬢様が一人で大丈夫かな…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.39,0:20:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That is, if she's even in Kawasaki.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.42,0:20:26.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アイツが川崎にいればの\Nハナシだけど…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.06,0:20:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I could search all night and not find her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.16,0:20:30.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いくら捜しても\N見つからねぇ…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.76,0:20:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She might've already gone home.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.89,0:20:33.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ひょっとしたら\Nもう家に帰ってるのかも…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.63,0:20:42.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ぐぐっ　落ちねぇ…\N何でだよーッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.40,0:20:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's not falling, why?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.60,0:20:44.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（頼朝）\N戯れは終わりじゃ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.64,0:20:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Playtime is over!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.30,0:20:45.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（衝撃音）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.81,0:20:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,KAWASAKI STATION
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.44,0:20:47.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）やめだやめ…！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.71,0:20:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.28,0:20:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was hopeless from the start.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.28,0:20:50.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,初めから無謀だったんだよ…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.61,0:20:54.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そう今回もまた\N俺の一人相撲…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.78,0:20:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right. I was just making{\i0}\N{\i1}one-sided presumptions again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.12,0:20:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As usual, a swing and a miss.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.15,0:20:58.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いつも通り\N空振りしちまった…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.03,0:21:06.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）ハァ…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.40,0:21:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to see Ono...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.46,0:21:10.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）\N大野と会いてーなぁ…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.93,0:21:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Haruo!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.96,0:21:11.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ガイル）\N春雄っ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.83,0:21:13.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おう？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.83,0:21:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.57,0:21:18.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ゲームキャラ一同）\N春雄ーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.87,0:21:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Haruo!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.87,0:21:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}-Haruo!{\i0}\N{\i1}-Haruo!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.47,0:21:21.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,♪〜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.18,0:21:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,GAME IN
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.81,0:21:28.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（男Ａ）す…　すげぇな…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.91,0:21:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Holy crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.22,0:21:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,She's already at 70 straight wins!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.35,0:21:30.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（男Ｂ）\Nもう70連勝にもなるぞ…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.75,0:21:32.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（男Ｃ）\N夕方からずっとこの調子だ…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.79,0:21:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,She's been going at this pace all evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.72,0:21:40.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（男Ｄ）こんなスゴイ子\N川崎にいたか？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.73,0:21:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Was there a girl this strong in Kawasaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.13,0:21:41.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（男Ｅ）いや…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.33,0:21:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.77,0:21:47.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（男Ｆ）あっちの子は\N言うまでもないが―
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.87,0:21:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That {\i1}Bishamon {\i0}player is pretty good,\Nbut no match for this girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.97,0:21:50.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今回のビシャモン使いも\Nなかなか…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.50,0:21:51.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（男Ｇ）うんうん
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.34,0:21:57.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（晶）…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.88,0:22:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez, your reflexes are ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.91,0:22:00.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）\Nったく なんつー反射神経だ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.95,0:22:03.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何をやってもガーキャンで\N跳ね返してきやがる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.98,0:22:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what I do,\Nit gets guard-cancelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.08,0:22:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're as unbelievable as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.15,0:22:06.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,相変わらずとんでもない\Nお嬢様だぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.32,0:22:08.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ようやっと見つけたぜ…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.45,0:22:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I've finally found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.39,0:22:10.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（晶）…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.12,0:22:14.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）所持金残り50円で\Nあの快挙を成し遂げてたのか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.23,0:22:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You managed all this with just\N50 yen left?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.73,0:22:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you plan to pay\Nfor the train home?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.76,0:22:18.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）帰りの電車賃\Nどーするつもりだったんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.70,0:22:21.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,飯でも食いに行くべ…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.77,0:22:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get some food.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.14,0:22:24.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（晶）…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.30,0:24:01.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,〜♪
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.48,0:24:14.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（春雄）\N知ってるか？　ドラクエの\N１作目で姫様を助けた後に―
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.01,0:24:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.11,0:24:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After saving the first princess{\i0}\N{\i1}in the first Dragon Quest,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.58,0:24:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}they stop at a hotel and spend the night{\i0}\N{\i1}before returning to the castle.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.68,0:24:17.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お城に帰らずに宿屋に寄って\Nそのまま泊まるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.85,0:24:21.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうすっと翌朝\N宿屋の主人が言うんだぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.89,0:24:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The next morning, the hotel owner says,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.62,0:24:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Seems like you had a good time{\i0}\N{\i1}last night." For real!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.66,0:24:24.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,〝昨夜は\Nお楽しみでしたねぇ〞って
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.03,0:24:27.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,♪〜
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.06,0:24:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Subtitle translation by\NEmily Noguchi
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.13,0:24:34.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,〜♪
